Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.10,0:41:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Zabalíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.67,0:41:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Jsi kufr,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.84,0:41:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,nebo ne?
